msgstr "3×3格合成台"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_crafting_table/init.lua:82
msgid ""
"A crafting table is a block which grants you access to a 3×3 crafting grid "
"which allows you to perform advanced crafts."
msgstr ""
"工作台是一种方块，能让你使用一个3×3的合成方格，便于你进行更高级的合成操作。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_crafting_table/init.lua:83
msgid "Rightclick the crafting table to access the 3×3 crafting grid."
msgstr "右键点击工作台以打开3×3的合成方格。"
